prmwqmw nwloN tu`ty hoey mnu`K ievyN hI hY, ijvyN s`p dI aumr hY (aumr qW lMmI hY, pr s`p sdw dUijAW nUM fMg hI mwrdw rihMdw hY[)
iesy qrHW prmwqmw nwloN tu`ty hoey mnu`K prmwqmw dw nwm Bulw ky ismrn qoN ibnw (ivArQ jIvn hI) jIaUNdy hn (mOkw bxn qy dUijAW nUM fMg hI mwrdy hn) ]1]
jyhVw iek A`K Jmkx ijqnw smw BI prmwqmw dy ismrn ivc guzwirAw jwey,
auh, mwno, l`KW kRoVW idn (jIaU ilAw, ikauNik ismrn dI brkiq nwl mnu`K dw Awqmk jIvn) sdw leI Afol ho jWdw hY ]1] rhwau]
pRBU-ismrn qoN KuMJ ky hor hor kMm krny iPtkwr-jog hI hn,
ijvyN kW dI cuMJ gMd ivc hI rihMdI hY, iqvyN ismrn-hIn mnu`KW dy mUMh (inMdw Awidk dy) gMd ivc hI rihMdy hn ]2]
pRBU dI Xwd qoN KuMJ ky mnu`K (loB qy kwmwidk ivc Ps ky) ku`iqAW vrgy kMmW ivc pRivrq rihMdy hn[
prmwqmw nwloN tuty hoey mnu`K vysvw iesqRIAW dy pu`qrW vWg (inl`j) ho jWdy hn ijn@W dy ipau dw nwm nhIN d`isAw jw skdw ]3]
prmwqmw dI Xwd qoN KuMJ ky auh (DrqI auqy Bwr hI hn, ijvyN) C`qirAW dy isr qy isMg;
prmwqmw nwloN tu`ty hoey mnu`K (sdw) JUT boldy hn, hr QW mukwlK hI K`tdy hn ]4]
ismrn qoN KuMJ ky auh Koqy vWg hI (mlIn jIvn guzwrdy hn, ijvyN Koqw sdw suAwh im`tI ivc lyt ky ^uS huMdw hY)
prmwqmw nwloN tu`ty hoey mnu`K (kukrmW vwly) gMdy QweIN hI iPrdy rihMdy hn ]5]
ismrn qoN KuMJ ky auh, mwno, hlky ku`qy bx jWdy hn (ijs nwl BI sMg krdy hn, aus nUM loB dw hlk cMboV dyNdy hn)
r`b nwloN tu`ty hoey mnu`K loB ivc gRsy rihMdy hn (auhnW dy rwh ivc, l`KW rupey kmw ky BI) rok nhIN pY skdI ]6]
r`b nwloN tu`tw hoieAw mnu`K ismrn qoN KuMJw rih ky Awqmk mOq shyV lYNdw hY,
auh sdw nIvyN kMmW vl rucI r`Kdw hY, aus dI nwh au~cI kul rih jWdI hY nwh au~cI jwiq ]7]
