gurU dy aupdyS auqy qur ky mYN sB qoN au~cI Awqmk AvsQw hwsl kr leI hY,
(dunIAw dy ivkwrW dy mukwbly qy) pUry gurU ny myrI ie`zq r`K leI hY ]1]
gurU dy aupdyS dI brkiq nwl mYN prmwqmw dw nwm ismirAw hY,
qy gurU dI ikrpw nwl mYnUM (prmwqmw dy crnW ivc) QW iml igAw hY (myrw mn pRBU-crnW ivc itikAw rihMdw hY) ]1] rhwau]
gurU dy aupdyS dI rwhIN (prmwqmw dI is&q-swlwh) sux ky mYN AwpxI jIB nwl BI is&q-swlwh aucwrdw rihMdw hW,
gurU dI ikrpw nwl Awqmk jIvn dyx vwlI is&q-swlwh dI bwxI myrI (rws-pUMjI bx geI hY) ]2]
gurU dy aupdyS dI brkiq nwl (myry AMdroN) myrw Awpw-Bwv imt igAw hY,
gurU dI dieAw nwl myrw bVw qyj-prqwp bx igAw hY (ik koeI ivkwr hux myry nyVy nhIN Fu`kdw) ]3]
gurU dy aupdyS qy qur ky myry mn dI Btkxw dUr ho geI hY,
qy hux mYN hr-QW-v`sdw prmwqmw vyK ilAw hY ]4]
gurU dy aupdyS dI brkiq nwl igRhsq ivc rih ky hI mYN pRBU-crnW dw imlwp mwx irhw hW[
gurU dI sMgq ivc (rih ky) swrw jgq hI (sMswr-smuMdr qoN) pwr lMG jWdw hY ]5]
gurU dy aupdyS qy qur ky myry swry kMmW ivc sPlqw ho rhI hY,
gurU dy aupdyS dI rwhIN mYN prmwqmw dw nwm hwsl kr ilAw hY (jo myry vwsqy sB kwmXwbIAW dw) ^zwnw hY ]6]
ijs ijs mnu`K ny myry gurU dI Aws (Awpxy mn ivc) Dwr leI hY,
aus dI jm dI PwhI k`tI geI hY ]7]
gurU dy aupdyS dI brkiq nwl myrI iksmq jwg peI hY,
mYnUM gurU imilAw hY (qy gurU dI imhr nwl) hy nwnk! mYnUM prmwqmw iml ipAw hY ]8]8]
