aus gurU nUM mYN (Awpxy) hryk swh dy nwl nwl cyqy krdw rihMdw hW,
jyhVw gurU myrI ijMd dw Awsrw hY myrI (Awqmk jIvn dI) rws-pUMjI (dw rwKw) hY ]1] rhwau]
ijauN ijauN mYN gurU dw drsn krdw hW, mYnUM Awqmk jIvn imldw hY[
ijauN ijauN mYN gurU dy crn DoNdw hW, mYnUM (Awqmk jIvn dyx vwlw) nwm-jl (pIx nUM, jpx nUM) imldw hY ]1]
gurU dy crnW dI DUV (myry vwsqy qIrQ dw jl hY aus) ivc mYN sdw ieSnwn krdw hW,
qy AnykW jnmW dI (iek`TI hoeI hoeI) haumY dI mYl (Awpxy mn ivcoN) dUr krdw hW ]2]
aus gurU nUM mYN p`Kw J`ldw hW,
ijs gurU ny mYnUM (ivkwrW dI) v`fI A`g qoN (Awpxw) h`Q dy ky bcwieAw hoieAw hY ]3]
mYN aus gurU dy Gr ivc (sdw) pwxI FoNdw hW,
ijs gurU pwsoN mYN aus prmwqmw dI sUJ-bUJ hwsl kIqI hY jyhVw kdy Gtdw vDdw nhIN ]4]
